/#
   A type describing the date from which each of the party may be allowed to terminate the trade.
 #/
record FpML5.recordkeeping.ReturnSwapEarlyTermination {
  # Reference to a party defined elsewhere in this document which may be allowed to terminate the trade.
  partyReference : FpML5.recordkeeping.PartyReference?

  # Specifies the date from which the early termination clause can be exercised.
  startingDate : FpML5.recordkeeping.StartingDate?

}

partyReference.Doc: Reference to a party defined elsewhere in this document which may be allowed to terminate the trade.
partyReference.Name: partyReference

startingDate.Doc: Specifies the date from which the early termination clause can be exercised.
startingDate.Name: startingDate
